Credits
=======

   Now I have to thank some people for supporting the development of
@{b}Scout@{ub} on many different kinds:

   @{b}*@{ub} Klaus `gizmo' Weber, he was always available to me and my many
     questions (not a few) during the programming of @{b}Scout@{ub}.

   @{b}*@{ub} Christian `cosinus' Stelter, he gave me the permission to use his
     many manuals.

   @{b}*@{ub} Stefan Stuntz for his great @{b}MagicUserInterface@{ub}

   @{b}*@{ub} all bug reporting and feature requesting people: Kai `wusel'
     Siering, Martin Hauner, Peter Meyer, Karl `Charly' Skibinski,
     Michael `Mick' Hohmann, Thore Böckelmann, Bernardo Innocenti, ...

     and last but not least

   @{b}*@{ub} all the others I've forgotten for reporting bugs, sending
     expansion boards data and so on.


@EndNode

